## Spec-side reading

- docs/model-routing-v1-spec.md §App A (lines ~575-595) — frozen
  RoutingDecision dataclass shape. Confirms `quota_state_at_decision`
  is the only quota-state carrier on the decision; no
  `advisor_disabled_reason` field.
- §4 (lines ~233-252) — guard rules. Post-CCW-5 body uses
  `advisor_model = NULL`, `source = 'quota_downgrade'`, and
  `reason = 'advisor disabled — overall quota ≥ 80%'`. The
  `advisor_disabled_reason` field has been struck.
- §8 (lines ~376-389) — override rate uses a 14-day rolling window
  with threshold 0.30.
- §9 (lines ~413-446) — API surface; `PATCH /api/routing/system/reorder`
  was added by CCW-5 (E-3 erratum). Implementation explicitly deferred
  to "feature 3 cleanup".
- §Errata E-1, E-2, E-3 (lines ~606-621) — three CCW-5 spec
  corrections, all shipped in commit 0036f7c1.

